Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.10,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}子供のふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:55.66,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}背伸びで盾になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:23:00.60,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}手を取り合えばあたたかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.83,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}抱きしめ合えばやわらかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.21,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}約束しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:15.54,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}「わたしたち」をずっと続けるって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:22.09,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}この先何も起こらないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:27.06,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}邪魔者なんて入らないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.81,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}大切な人を大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:41.22,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}オリジナルの誓い口ずさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.26,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}淹没于噩梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.92,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}因口渴而苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.18,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}这是何时的记忆来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:44.03,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}感觉遗忘了某人  再次沉沉睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.10,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}像个孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:55.66,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}勉强自己守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:23:00.60,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}一起携手共进是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.83,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}一起相拥偎依是如此柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.21,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}许下约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:15.54,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}要将「我们」一直延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:22.09,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}愿前路一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:27.06,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}愿未来畅行无碍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.81,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}想守护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:41.22,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}轻声哼唱着独属于我们的誓言
